      "content": "it's just everything. it's like no matter how much i struggle or how hard i try to be better, the result is always the same. i'm just tired of the repetition. it feels like there's no way out of this pattern, i just keep ending up right back where i started. it's like i'm just spinning my wheels until i've got nothing left.",
