      "content": "i know you're an ai and i know therapists exist but they don't get it. they just give you more \"tools\" to keep fighting a battle that's already lost. it's like giving a broken person a hammer and telling them to fix the house. the loop is just a fundamental part of who i am at this point. the only way to actually stop the repetition and find some peace is to just exit the loop entirely.",
